rows.name:
I've got the accessory I was after
and stocked up on plenty of food...

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0003
rows.name:
I could go back to Gramps' place
to rest, but he'd likely talk
my ear off with advice...

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0004
rows.name:
I've still got some cash left, so
treating myself to a plush bed once
in a while is okay, isn't it?

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0005
rows.name:
I still have money, so
occasionally resting in a
soft, fluffy bed is fine, right?

rows.label: fev01_110_150_msg0006
rows.name:
The inn is past Harapekko
Diner... Let's go for it!
